  "title": "returning to God",
  "comment": "Scripture declares that all humanity has turned away from God, and must return to him. The term ``repentance'' is often used to refer to this process of returning to God and the inward and outward changes that it demands of people. Scripture also indicates that believers can wander away from God; they too must return to him.",
